\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Cross-region generalization on NDWS. Lift = AUC-PR / pos\_frac is the appropriate cross-distribution comparison since positive-class density differs by $7\times $ across regions. PI-GNODE achieves $\sim $11$\times $ lift in all four cells, indicating clean transfer.}}{5}{table.caption.10}\protected@file@percent }
